                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1097-18430227 t18430227-1097-punishment-239"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>There were two other indictments against the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
